@daddewey @dwsingleton1280 @GettinSome82 @chricolv @johnflynn20
 Make sure your Google Play Store app is up to date. It should be version 8.3.73 or later. In Settings -> Display -> Screen Resolution, make sure you are running at FHD+ or WQHD+ resolution (not HD+ resolution). In Settings -> Apps -> Google Play Store -> Storage, tap Clear Data. Only clearing the cache is not enough. Reboot the device before retrying the game
I have seen these steps work for players recently, let us know if that is the case for you too, thanks.
